column6: In the first two weeks of August 2009/N. N.
column12:
The victim was attacked at night in the street by a group of strangers who beat her up severely. She died in hospital.

She was a young trans woman who had a degree from the Algiers University, but after being abandoned by her family had no choice but to earn a living as a sex worker.

Her exact date of death is unknown, but it was sometime in the first two weeks of August.

Tyli'a (who was also known as NaNa Boo) was one of two transgender people stabbed on the street and brought to hospital.

One died in hospital, but the other was expected to recover. The police investigated the death as a possible hate crime.

Note that tdor.info give her age as 18.

Examiner, 01.09.2009

Paulina was stabbed to death inside her apartment in East Hollywood. The suspected murderer is a homeless person who was known to frequent transgender sex workers.
